Now I want to back up and look at verse number 7.

00:02:58.360 --> 00:03:03.279
The Bible says this here, O my people, and I will speak, O Israel, and I will testify

00:03:03.279 --> 00:03:04.399
against thee.

00:03:04.399 --> 00:03:08.199
Notice this, I am God, even thy God.

00:03:08.199 --> 00:03:12.679
