00:05:56.320 --> 00:06:03.000
And we find that he speaks in that text of Scripture in Psalm 34 about all his troubles.

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:06.920
This evening as we think about the presence of trouble, and we consider that, again I

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:11.660
