00:06:38.720 --> 00:06:41.959
He knows when it's going to come before we know that it's going to come.

00:06:41.959 --> 00:06:43.239
He's aware of it.

00:06:43.239 --> 00:06:47.600
And the thing that's amazing to me is that as I look at the passage of Scripture that

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:53.239
is before us, I would say that He instructs us, but we also could say that He invites

00:06:53.239 --> 00:06:58.880
us that during that time of trouble, we're to call upon Him.

00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:00.119
We're to call upon Him.

00:07:00.119 --> 00:07:05.640
Now, I'm sure that at some point in your life, I know it's happened in my own life, not only

00:07:05.640 --> 00:07:11.519
