00:08:19.880 --> 00:08:24.440
but for some reason, there was some level of apprehension on your part, I don't want

00:08:24.440 --> 00:08:29.160
to put them out, I don't want to bother them, I don't want to fill in the blank, right?

00:08:29.160 --> 00:08:33.640
We joke in our home where there are times in which somebody is trying to do something,

