00:14:22.680 --> 00:14:24.720
and all that's taken place,

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:27.920
he follows the instruction of his father

00:14:27.920 --> 00:14:29.240
and he goes and he does that,

00:14:29.240 --> 00:14:30.240
which he's supposed to do.

00:14:30.240 --> 00:14:32.360
And we find that there's a number of difficulties

00:14:32.360 --> 00:14:34.800
that face Joseph in his life.

00:14:34.800 --> 00:14:37.320
And I want you to notice at the end of his life

00:14:37.320 --> 00:14:39.600
here in Genesis chapter number 50,

00:14:39.600 --> 00:14:42.200
that the brethren get together in verse number 15.

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:43.760
Now, dad has died,

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:45.120
the burial's taken place,

00:14:45.120 --> 00:14:46.920
they're now back in Egypt.

00:14:46.920 --> 00:14:47.760
And the Bible says,

00:14:47.760 --> 00:14:49.960
and when Joseph's brethren saw that their father was dead,

00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:53.040
they said, Joseph will peradventure hate us

00:14:53.040 --> 00:14:55.240
and will certainly requite us all the evil

00:14:55.240 --> 00:14:58.440
which we did unto him.

00:14:58.440 --> 00:15:00.640
And they sent a messenger unto Joseph saying,

00:15:00.640 --> 00:15:03.440
thy father did command before he died saying,

00:15:03.440 --> 00:15:05.000
so shall you say unto Joseph,

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:06.280
forgive, I pray thee now,

00:15:06.280 --> 00:15:08.880
the trespass of thy brethren and their sin,

00:15:08.880 --> 00:15:10.640
for they did unto the evil.

00:15:10.640 --> 00:15:11.800
And now we pray thee,

00:15:11.800 --> 00:15:13.640
forgive the trespass of thy servants

00:15:13.640 --> 00:15:15.120
and the God of thy father,

00:15:15.120 --> 00:15:16.560
of the God of thy father.

00:15:16.560 --> 00:15:19.040
And Joseph wept when they spake unto him.

00:15:20.200 --> 00:15:22.880
And his brethren also went and fell down before his face

00:15:22.880 --> 00:15:24.760
and they said, behold, we be thy servants.

00:15:24.760 --> 00:15:27.840
And notice the response of Joseph in verse number 19.

00:15:27.840 --> 00:15:29.000
And Joseph said unto them,

00:15:29.000 --> 00:15:33.640
fear not, for am I in the place of God.

00:15:33.640 --> 00:15:36.200
But as for you, you thought evil against me,

00:15:36.200 --> 00:15:39.420
but God meant it unto good

00:15:39.420 --> 00:15:41.540
to bring to pass as it is this day

00:15:41.540 --> 00:15:44.100
to save much people alive.

00:15:44.100 --> 00:15:45.880
I don't know if you've ever really meditated

00:15:45.880 --> 00:15:50.120
upon what Joseph says in verse 19 and 20

00:15:50.120 --> 00:15:52.200
in this passage of Scripture.

00:15:52.200 --> 00:15:53.360
But when Joseph says,

00:15:53.360 --> 00:15:56.000
but as for you, you thought evil against me,

00:15:56.000 --> 00:15:58.320
you can understand what he's speaking about

00:15:58.320 --> 00:16:00.760
contextually as you understand the life of Joseph

00:16:00.760 --> 00:16:02.280
and the way in which his brethren,

00:16:02.280 --> 00:16:03.320
they were going to kill him.

00:16:03.320 --> 00:16:04.600
They put him in the pit, right?

00:16:04.600 --> 00:16:05.720
They were going to kill him

00:16:05.720 --> 00:16:07.880
and let him starve there, let him die.

00:16:07.880 --> 00:16:11.200
They saw the merchant men that were coming.

00:16:11.200 --> 00:16:13.400
They sold him into bondage.

00:16:13.440 --> 00:16:16.200
And we find that they meant it unto evil.

00:16:16.200 --> 00:16:17.840
They had no good intentions

00:16:17.840 --> 00:16:19.120
with regard to their brother.

00:16:19.120 --> 00:16:22.920
In fact, what motivated the decisions that they made

00:16:22.920 --> 00:16:24.920
were the dreams that he dreamed.

00:16:24.920 --> 00:16:26.680
And they said, let's see what will become

00:16:26.680 --> 00:16:30.440
of this dreamer.

00:16:30.440 --> 00:16:33.560
But Joseph says God meant it unto good.

00:16:33.560 --> 00:16:36.520
You understand all that Joseph dealt with?

00:16:36.520 --> 00:16:39.840
You understand that Joseph was in the pit.

00:16:39.840 --> 00:16:40.880
He was out of that pit.

00:16:40.880 --> 00:16:42.800
He was sent into Egypt

00:16:42.840 --> 00:16:47.520
and became a servant there at Potiphar's house.

00:16:47.520 --> 00:16:49.360
He prospered.

00:16:49.360 --> 00:16:52.440
Why? Because he lived in the presence of God

00:16:52.440 --> 00:16:55.640
and he sought to please God and he prospered.

00:16:55.640 --> 00:16:58.320
But there was a day in which Potiphar's wife

00:16:58.320 --> 00:17:00.520
continually came to him and came to him

00:17:00.520 --> 00:17:02.560
and we find that she lied about him

00:17:02.560 --> 00:17:04.040
and he's then imprisoned.

00:17:04.040 --> 00:17:05.560
And they're in prison

00:17:05.560 --> 00:17:07.400
and he's there for an extended period of time

00:17:07.400 --> 00:17:09.400
and the butler and the baker come

00:17:09.400 --> 00:17:11.520
and he interprets their dreams

00:17:11.520 --> 00:17:12.960
and the butler and the baker

00:17:12.960 --> 00:17:15.480
have their dreams come to pass

00:17:15.480 --> 00:17:17.840
just as Joseph had interpreted

00:17:17.840 --> 00:17:20.000
and he said to the butler, remember me?

00:17:20.000 --> 00:17:21.440
But he forgot him.

00:17:21.440 --> 00:17:23.960
Two years go by.

00:17:23.960 --> 00:17:25.720
Eventually, Joseph gets to the palace.

00:17:25.720 --> 00:17:27.040
He's in a great position.

00:17:27.040 --> 00:17:28.480
He has great authority.

00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:30.880
Only Pharaoh was greater than him in the throne.

00:17:30.880 --> 00:17:32.800
But you understand there were some periods

00:17:32.800 --> 00:17:34.520
of difficulty that he faced.

00:17:34.520 --> 00:17:36.560
There were some times of trouble.

00:17:36.560 --> 00:17:39.440
I want you to notice what Stephen,

00:17:39.440 --> 00:17:41.120
the martyr in the New Testament,

00:17:41.720 --> 00:17:42.640
I want you to notice what he says

00:17:42.640 --> 00:17:45.160
when he's preaching in Acts chapter number seven

00:17:45.160 --> 00:17:48.880
and what a great passage of scripture here

00:17:48.880 --> 00:17:50.720
in the book of Acts in the seventh chapter

00:17:50.720 --> 00:17:53.080
and to hear this sermon of Stephen

00:17:53.080 --> 00:17:56.360
