00:18:26.160 --> 00:18:28.120
sold Joseph into Egypt.

00:18:28.120 --> 00:18:32.440
Notice these next words, but God was with him.

00:18:33.600 --> 00:18:37.000
Oh, would you find comfort in that truth this evening?

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:38.280
He was in a foreign land.

00:18:38.600 --> 00:18:39.440
He was in Egypt.

00:18:39.440 --> 00:18:41.679
They were a polytheistic people.

00:18:41.679 --> 00:18:43.960
I mean, let's just be honest about the situation

00:18:43.960 --> 00:18:45.280
in which he finds himself.

00:18:45.280 --> 00:18:49.840
He's a young man and he's there all alone

00:18:49.840 --> 00:18:51.280
and his father and his brethren

00:18:51.280 --> 00:18:53.840
and all that he knows is separated from him

00:18:53.840 --> 00:18:55.559
and he's there in that foreign land,

00:18:55.559 --> 00:18:58.200
in that polytheistic, heathen land,

00:18:58.200 --> 00:19:01.559
but God was with him.

00:19:01.559 --> 00:19:05.559
And it says this, and delivered him

00:19:06.559 --> 00:19:11.559
out of all his afflictions and gave him favor and wisdom

00:19:12.440 --> 00:19:14.960
