00:19:14.960 --> 00:19:18.799
and made him governor over Egypt and all his house.

00:19:18.799 --> 00:19:20.440
And if we're not careful this evening,

00:19:20.440 --> 00:19:22.799
here's what we say in light of Joseph.

00:19:22.799 --> 00:19:25.720
It would say, yeah, but he was in the palace.

00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:28.239
We forget about the two years he was in the prison,

00:19:28.239 --> 00:19:29.799
really longer than two years

00:19:29.799 --> 00:19:32.080
because he was forgotten for two years.

00:19:32.080 --> 00:19:33.200
We forget about that.

00:19:33.200 --> 00:19:35.200
Listen, two years is a long time.

00:19:35.320 --> 00:19:36.799
Amen?

00:19:36.799 --> 00:19:40.160
And we think about, oh, we understand the end

00:19:40.160 --> 00:19:43.520
because it's history and we read the entirety of his life

00:19:43.520 --> 00:19:44.600
in just a few moments.

00:19:44.600 --> 00:19:46.720
I mean, you can sit down this evening

00:19:46.720 --> 00:19:48.320
and before you pillow your head,

00:19:48.320 --> 00:19:51.320
