00:20:01.580 --> 00:20:03.160
before you pillow your head.

00:20:03.160 --> 00:20:04.820
And you can know from the beginning

00:20:04.820 --> 00:20:06.280
to the end of his life.

00:20:06.280 --> 00:20:07.700
And what we fail to realize

00:20:07.700 --> 00:20:09.280
