00:20:09.280 --> 00:20:10.320
the same way we do,

00:20:10.320 --> 00:20:12.800
one day at a time.

00:20:12.800 --> 00:20:14.360
God was with him.

00:20:14.360 --> 00:20:16.280
And the testimony is this,

00:20:16.280 --> 00:20:19.800
