00:20:19.800 --> 00:20:21.040
Gave him favor and wisdom

00:20:21.040 --> 00:20:22.400
in the sight of Pharaoh, king of Egypt.

00:20:22.400 --> 00:20:23.920
Listen, when we're dealing with trouble

00:20:23.920 --> 00:20:25.520
and difficulty and adversity,

00:20:25.520 --> 00:20:29.040
