00:21:04.600 --> 00:21:06.480
and the children of Israel as a whole.

00:21:06.480 --> 00:21:08.800
As you think about the deliverance of God,

00:21:08.800 --> 00:21:11.240
how that there were times of difficulty,

00:21:11.240 --> 00:21:13.120
of adversity, of trouble,

00:21:13.120 --> 00:21:15.760
and they call out to God and God blesses

00:21:15.760 --> 00:21:19.680
and God delivers and He's there to help His people.

00:21:19.680 --> 00:21:21.440
We've mentioned already about David.

